'''Magnepulse bombs''' were a piece of equipment carried aboard the [[inquisition module]] of a [[modular taskforce cruiser]].<ref name="DESB">''[[Dark Empire Sourcebook]]''</ref> It was a clean weapon that prevented the enemy from retaliating with modern weaponry. The bombs were the same size as a standard [[TIE series/Legends|TIE Series]] [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]], and any [[Starship/Legends|starship]] capable of carrying fighters could transport magnepulse bombs. It was a one-shot weapon, meaning it was mission expensive due to the sophisticated technology.

